Actually, my drums and sound effects work exactly the same way too, as drums are much like sound effects. The only difference is priority. Here are the levels of priority for my music:<br /><br />Lowest:<br />Square Music<br />Triangle Music<br /><br />Middle:<br />Drums<br /><br />Highest:<br />Sound Effects<br /><br />So Sound Effects will overwrite the drums, and drums will overwrite music.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=138">Celius</a> — Sat Apr 18, 2009 9:48 am</p><hr />
